casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Lawrence.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Lawrence (1991), 57 Ohio St. 3d 609.]

(No. 90-1958 Submitted January 9, 1991 Decided January 16, 1991.)

The resignation of Herbert Lee Lawrence as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
